	X_t  = A_1 X_{t-1} + ... + A_k X_{t-k} + rest + epsilon_t, epsilon_t ~ N(0,Omega),

	Z0_t = Pi Z1_t + Phi Z2_t + rest* + epsilon_t, epsilon_t ~ N(0,Omega),

	Z0_t = Pi Z1_t + Phi Z2_t + rest* + epsilon_t, epsilon_t ~ N(0,Omega),

I(1) ESTIMATES FOR RANK 1:
